[
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">gathered</st> <st data-num=\"0376 0259\">together</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">in</st> the <st data-num=\"07339\" class=\"\">plaza</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">which</st> was <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">in front of</st> the <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">Water</st> <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">Gate</st>. They <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">asked</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05830\" class=\"\">Ezra</st> the <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">scribe</st> to <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> the <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">book</st> of the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st> of <st data-num=\"04872\" class=\"\">Moses</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">which</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> had <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">commanded</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"05830\" class=\"\">Ezra</st> the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought</st> the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> the <st data-num=\"06951\" class=\"\">assembly</st> which included <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">women</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> those able to <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">understand</st> what they <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st>. (This happened on the <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">first</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> of the <st data-num=\"07637\" class=\"\">seventh</st> <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">month</st>.) ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "So he <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">read</st> it <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> the <st data-num=\"07339\" class=\"\">plaza</st> <st data-num=\"0834 06440\">in front of</st> the <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">Water</st> <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">Gate</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"0216\" class=\"\">dawn</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">till</st> <st data-num=\"04276 03117\">noon</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">before</st> the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> and <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">women</st> and those children who could <st data-num=\"0241\" class=\"\">understand</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> were <st data-num=\"0241 0413\">eager to hear</st><n id=\"3\" /> the <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">book</st> of the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"05830\" class=\"\">Ezra</st> the <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">scribe</st> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stood</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> a <st data-num=\"04026\" class=\"\">towering</st> <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">wooden</st> <st data-num=\"04026\" class=\"\">platform</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0834 06213\">constructed</st> for this <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">purpose</st>. <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">Standing</st> <st data-num=\"0681\" class=\"\">near</st> him <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> his <st data-num=\"03225\" class=\"\">right</st> were <st data-num=\"04993\" class=\"\">Mattithiah</st>, <st data-num=\"08087\" class=\"\">Shema</st>, <st data-num=\"06043\" class=\"\">Anaiah</st>, <st data-num=\"0223\" class=\"\">Uriah</st>, <st data-num=\"02518\" class=\"\">Hilkiah</st>, and <st data-num=\"04641\" class=\"\">Masseiah</st>. On his <st data-num=\"08040\" class=\"\">left</st> were <st data-num=\"06305\" class=\"\">Pedaiah</st>, <st data-num=\"04332\" class=\"\">Mishael</st>, <st data-num=\"04441\" class=\"\">Malkijah</st>, <st data-num=\"02828\" class=\"\">Hashum</st>, <st data-num=\"02806\" class=\"\">Hashbaddanah</st>, <st data-num=\"02148\" class=\"\">Zechariah</st>, and <st data-num=\"04918\" class=\"\">Meshullam</st>. ",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"05830\" class=\"\">Ezra</st> <st data-num=\"06605\" class=\"\">opened</st> the <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">book</st> in <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">plain view</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> he <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> elevated <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">above</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>. When he <st data-num=\"06605\" class=\"\">opened</st> the book,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stood up</st>.",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"05830\" class=\"\">Ezra</st> <st data-num=\"01288\" class=\"\">blessed</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, the <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"06030\" class=\"\">replied</st> \u201c<st data-num=\"0543\" class=\"\">Amen</st>! <st data-num=\"0543\" class=\"\">Amen</st>!\u201d as they <st data-num=\"04607\" class=\"\">lifted</st> their <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hands</st>. Then they <st data-num=\"06915\" class=\"\">bowed down</st> and <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">worshiped</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> with their <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">faces</st> to the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03442\" class=\"\">Jeshua,</st> <st data-num=\"01137\" class=\"\">Bani</st>, <st data-num=\"08274\" class=\"\">Sherebiah</st>, <st data-num=\"03226\" class=\"\">Jamin</st>, <st data-num=\"06126\" class=\"\">Akkub</st>, <st data-num=\"07678\" class=\"\">Shabbethai</st>, <st data-num=\"01941\" class=\"\">Hodiah</st>, <st data-num=\"04641\" class=\"\">Maaseiah</st>, <st data-num=\"07042\" class=\"\">Kelita</st>, <st data-num=\"05838\" class=\"\">Azariah</st>, <st data-num=\"03107\" class=\"\">Jozabad</st>, <st data-num=\"02605\" class=\"\">Hanan</st>, and <st data-num=\"06411\" class=\"\">Pelaiah</st>\u2014all of whom were <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st><n id=\"1\" />\u2014were <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">teaching</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st>, as the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">remained</st> <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">standing</st>. ",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">read</st> from the <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">book</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st>, <st data-num=\"06567\" class=\"\">explaining</st> it<n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">imparting</st> <st data-num=\"07922\" class=\"\">insight</st>. Thus the people<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">gained understanding</st> from <st data-num=\"04744\" class=\"\">what was read</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"05166\" class=\"\">Nehemiah</st> the <st data-num=\"01931 08660\">governor</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05830\" class=\"\">Ezra</st> the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priestly</st> <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">scribe</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> and the <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st> who were <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">imparting understanding</st> to the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">them</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> \u201cThis <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">is</st> <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">holy</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"056\" class=\"\">mourn</st> <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">weep</st>.\u201d <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> had been <st data-num=\"01058\" class=\"\">weeping</st> when they <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">words</st> of the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st>. ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to them, \u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Go</st> and <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat</st> <st data-num=\"04924\" class=\"\">delicacies</st> and <st data-num=\"08354\" class=\"\">drink</st> <st data-num=\"04477\" class=\"\">sweet drinks</st> and <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">send</st> <st data-num=\"04490\" class=\"\">portions</st> to those for whom <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">nothing is</st> <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">prepared</st>. <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> this <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> is <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">holy</st> to our <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06087\" class=\"\">grieve</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"02304\" class=\"\">joy</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">is</st> your <st data-num=\"04581\" class=\"\">strength</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then the <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st> <st data-num=\"02814\" class=\"\">quieted</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02013\" class=\"\">Be quiet</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> this <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> is <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">holy</st>. Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06087\" class=\"\">grieve</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">departed</st> to <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat</st> and <st data-num=\"08354\" class=\"\">drink</st> and to <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">share</st> their <st data-num=\"04490\" class=\"\">food</st><n id=\"1\" /> with others<n id=\"2\" /> and to <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">enjoy</st> <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">tremendous</st> <st data-num=\"08057\" class=\"\">joy</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> they had <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">gained insight</st> in the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">matters</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">had</st> been <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">made known</st> to them.</p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">On the <st data-num=\"08145\" class=\"\">second</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> of the month the <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">family</st> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">leaders</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">met</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">with</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05830\" class=\"\">Ezra</st> the <st data-num=\"05608\" class=\"\">scribe</st>, together with <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>, the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st>, and the <st data-num=\"03881\" class=\"\">Levites</st>, to <st data-num=\"07919 0413\">consider</st> the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">words</st> of the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st>. ",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">discovered</st> <st data-num=\"03789\" class=\"\">written</st> in the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> had <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">commanded</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">through</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04872\" class=\"\">Moses</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> should <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in <st data-num=\"05521\" class=\"\">temporary shelters</st> during the <st data-num=\"02282\" class=\"\">festival</st> of the <st data-num=\"07637\" class=\"\">seventh</st> <st data-num=\"02320\" class=\"\">month</st>, ",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "and <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> they should <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">make a proclamation</st> and <st data-num=\"05674 0559\">disseminate</st> this <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">message</st><n id=\"1\" /> in <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> their <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st> and in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>:<n id=\"2\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">Go</st> to the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">hill country</st> and <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring back</st> <st data-num=\"02132\" class=\"\">olive</st> <st data-num=\"05929\" class=\"\">branches</st> and <st data-num=\"05929\" class=\"\">branches</st> of <st data-num=\"08081\" class=\"\">wild olive</st> <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">trees</st>, <st data-num=\"01918\" class=\"\">myrtle trees</st>, <st data-num=\"08558\" class=\"\">date palms</st>, and other <st data-num=\"05687\" class=\"\">leafy</st> <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">trees</st> to <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">construct</st> <st data-num=\"05521\" class=\"\">temporary shelters</st>, as it is <st data-num=\"03789\" class=\"\">written</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">went out</st> and <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought</st> these things<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">back</st> and <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">constructed</st> <st data-num=\"05521\" class=\"\">temporary shelters</st> for <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">themselves</st>, <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">each</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> his <st data-num=\"01406\" class=\"\">roof</st> and in his <st data-num=\"02691\" class=\"\">courtyard</st> and in the <st data-num=\"02691\" class=\"\">courtyards</st> of the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st><n id=\"2\" /> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> and in the <st data-num=\"07339\" class=\"\">plaza</st> of the <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">Water</st> <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">Gate</st> and the <st data-num=\"07339\" class=\"\">plaza</st> of the <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st> <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">Gate</st>. ",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"06951\" class=\"\">assembly</st> which had <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">returned</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"07628\" class=\"\">exile</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">constructed</st> <st data-num=\"05521\" class=\"\">temporary shelters</st> and <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">lived</st> in <st data-num=\"05521\" class=\"\">them</st>. The <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> had <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st> <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">so</st> from the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st> of <st data-num=\"03442\" class=\"\">Joshua</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"05126\" class=\"\">Nun</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>. Everyone <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">experienced</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"08057\" class=\"\">joy</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nehemiah",
    "chapter": "8",
    "text": "Ezra<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">read</st> in the <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">book</st> of the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> by <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>, <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">first</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"03117 0314\">last</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> They <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">observed</st> the <st data-num=\"02282\" class=\"\">festival</st> for <st data-num=\"07651\" class=\"\">seven</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st>, and on the <st data-num=\"08066\" class=\"\">eighth</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> they held an <st data-num=\"06116\" class=\"\">assembly</st><n id=\"3\" /> as was <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">required</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  }
]